Maintainer: PCManX Development Group <pcmanx@googlegroups.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), autotools-dev, intltool, libgtk2.0-dev, libnotify-dev, xulrunner-1.9.2-dev, libx11-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
